# One Spotify playlist URL per line. Blank lines and #-comments ignored.
# spotiflac extracts the playlist ID from the URL, so any of these forms work:
#   https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DXcBWIGoYBM5M
#   https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DXcBWIGoYBM5M?si=abc123
#
# Order doesn't matter — the batch driver processes playlists in URL-sort order
# and tracks completion in $SPOTIFLAC_STATE_DIR/done.txt.

https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DXcBWIGoYBM5M
https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1E37jmRfNgFn7K
